# 📅 Week 1: Introduction to Python

Welcome to the first week of the Python learning journey! This week focuses on getting familiar with the basics of Python and setting up the foundation for everything to come.

## 📘 Topics Covered
- What is Python?
- Installing Python and setting up the environment
- Writing your first Python script
- Basic syntax and structure
- Variables and data types
- Comments and formatting

## 🛠️ Practice
- Simple print statements
- Using variables to store and display data
- Writing and running basic Python programs

## 🎯 Goals
- Understand what Python is and why it's useful
- Successfully install Python and a code editor (e.g., VS Code)
- Write and run your first few lines of code

---

Ready to dive in? Let’s write some Python! 🐍



